        "value": "<div class=\"project-closing-section\">\n  <div class=\"closing-card\">\n    <span class=\"closing-badge\">ФИНАЛ КЕЙСА</span>\n    <h2 class=\"closing-title\">СПАСИБО ЗА ПРОСМОТР!</h2>\n    <p class=\"closing-lead\">Благодарю за внимание к проекту! Открыт для обсуждения новых 3D-проектов, разработки интерактивных приложений на Unreal Engine 5 и коммерческого сотрудничества.</p>\n    <div class=\"closing-contacts-grid\">\n      <a href=\"https://t.me/Saske_2k18\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"closing-contact-item hoverable\">\n        <div class=\"contact-icon\">\n          <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M21.5 2L2 9.5l7 3 3 7 3.5-5.5L20 18l1.5-16z\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"contact-meta\">\n          <span class=\"contact-type\">Telegram</span>\n          <span class=\"contact-val\">@Saske_2k18</span>\n        </div>\n      </a>\n      <a href=\"mailto:shcherbinindaniil@gmail.com\" class=\"closing-contact-item hoverable\">\n        <div class=\"contact-icon\">\n          <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z\"/><polyline points=\"22,6 12,13 2,6\"/></svg>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"contact-meta\">\n          <span class=\"contact-type\">Email</span>\n          <span class=\"contact-val\">shcherbinindaniil@gmail.com</span>\n        </div>\n      </a>\n      <a href=\"tel:+79029397362\" class=\"closing-contact-item hoverable\">\n        <div class=\"contact-icon\">\n          <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"><path d=\"M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 1